div.span:
Is your system linear
or are you solving a regulation problem
and can linearize a nonlinear model?
Do you have a SISO system?

Use MPC or proceed
further down with gain scheduling.
Do you have a SIMO system?

Consider using a
Cascaded PID controller

Is the system square and
has weakly interacting loops?

Consider independent
PID controllers
possibly with a decoupler

Include a disturbance model
in the controller

Do you have tight constraints on
inputs, states or outputs?

Are you solving a
reference-tracking problem?
Consider using an LQG, H2 or H-inf controller
